僵尸吞下。随后会返回并咀嚼，最后将僵尸的头颅吐向敌人。"},"Special":[],"Chat":{"en":"\"I'm a picky eater, I'll admit it,\" admits Snap Pea casually. \"I'll eat a zombie, no problem, but there's just something about heads. I feel like they're looking at me.\"","zh":"“我承认，我吃东西挺挑剔的，”大嘴豌豆随口承认道。“吃个僵尸没问题，但就是觉得脑袋这东西吧……总感觉它们在看着我。”"},"DisplayOffset":{"x":0,"y":0},"BriefIntroduction":{"en":"Eats zombies and spits out their heads","zh":"吃掉僵尸并吐出他们的头颅"}}}}